            "title": "Solar Battery Cost Guide 2026: USA & UK Prices Analyzed",
            "description": "How much should you really pay for storage in 2026? We break down installed costs, hardware prices, and the ROI entitlement for homeowners in the US and UK.",
            "updated": "2026-02-13",
